=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598", "stars": 4628, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 172169, "username": "alexkuang", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/alexkuang", "website": "kuang.dev", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "Austin, Texas", "tagline": "国家二级保护废物", "bio": "邮箱： eW9Aa3VhbmcuZGV2Cg==", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b1214569608318ec38d20c9a5925d1fb?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b1214569608318ec38d20c9a5925d1fb?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b1214569608318ec38d20c9a5925d1fb?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1462686650, "last_modified": 1649723634}, "last_reply_by": "hawei", "last_touched": 1653203770, "title": "Raycast 真不错 Alfred 已卸载", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/854364", "created": 1653127030, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1653127030, "replies": 43, "id": 854364}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_large.png?m=1650127482", "name": "shanghai", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_normal.png?m=1650127482", "title": "上海", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai", "topics": 2845, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shanghai", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1650127482", "stars": 2043, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 18, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 340461, "username": "jaggle", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jaggle", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4fbd0d76e735c216ba7a35ba2feb90c7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4fbd0d76e735c216ba7a35ba2feb90c7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4fbd0d76e735c216ba7a35ba2feb90c7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1534014183, "last_modified": 1653141849}, "last_reply_by": "phithon", "last_touched": 1653209183, "title": "魔都（疫情期间）房租即将涨价 500，可以根据民法典第一百八十条拒签合同吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/854385", "created": 1653142512, "deleted": 0, "content": "民法典原文：\r\n\r\n> 第一百八十条  因不可抗力不能履行民事义务的，不承担民事责任。法律另有规定的，依照其规定。\r\n\r\n> 不可抗力是不能预见、不能避免且不能克服的客观情况。\r\n\r\n\r\n**现在这家公司（某爱某家）要求涨房租 500 ，其中包含 4.8 个百分点的服务费，我认为不合理：**\r\n\r\n**房租涨价，我有搬家的自由，不能因为疫情搬不了家，我就只能被迫接受不合理的涨价**\r\n\r\n**对方后面说可以按新的价格续租一个月。**\r\n\r\n**我依然回复表示不会接受，只接受原价续租一个月**\r\n\r\n**对方说到时候不续合同，且不搬走的话，发律师函并让我交违约金(是否吓唬我？)**\r\n\r\n**根据上面民法典这一条，能否怼回去并拿下胜算？**\r\n\r\n**懂法的兄弟们帮忙参谋参谋，感激！**\r\n\r\n\r\n另外魔都房租涨价是常态吗？总不能一直涨吧？我现在算下新出生的小宝宝一家 4 口人，搬家也挺烦的。万一是普涨呢，搬了也还是这个价的话，搬家又得不偿失。\r\n\r\n漂泊的打工人，难啊！", "content_rendered": "<p>民法典原文：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>第一百八十条  因不可抗力不能履行民事义务的，不承担民事责任。法律另有规定的，依照其规定。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>不可抗力是不能预见、不能避免且不能克服的客观情况。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>现在这家公司（某爱某家）要求涨房租 500 ，其中包含 4.8 个百分点的服务费，我认为不合理：</strong></p>\n<p><strong>房租涨价，我有搬家的自由，不能因为疫情搬不了家，我就只能被迫接受不合理的涨价</strong></p>\n<p><strong>对方后面说可以按新的价格续租一个月。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>我依然回复表示不会接受，只接受原价续租一个月</strong></p>\n<p><strong>对方说到时候不续合同，且不搬走的话，发律师函并让我交违约金(是否吓唬我？)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>根据上面民法典这一条，能否怼回去并拿下胜算？</strong></p>\n<p><strong>懂法的兄弟们帮忙参谋参谋，感激！</strong></p>\n<p>另外魔都房租涨价是常态吗？总不能一直涨吧？我现在算下新出生的小宝宝一家 4 口人，搬家也挺烦的。万一是普涨呢，搬了也还是这个价的话，搬家又得不偿失。</p>\n<p>漂泊的打工人，难啊！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1653142512, "replies": 41, "id": 854385}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 1064, "f